	* _.ypk: version 0.0.10.
	
	* diff1: Added --quiet option.

2011-09-05  Masatake YAMATO  <yamato@redhat.com>

	* _.ypk: version 0.0.9.

	* diff1 (diff1_package): Ignore directories
	listed in rpm -ql.

2011-09-01  Masatake YAMATO  <yamato@redhat.com>

	* _.ypk: version 0.0.8.

	* opm: New file.

2011-08-16  Masatake YAMATO  <yamato@redhat.com>

	* _.ypk: Added url.

	* diff1 (mtime): Don't use it when --package mode.
	(print_usage): Added more examples.
	(parse_arguments): Use # as prefix for some of error messages.
	(diff1_package): Use rpm -ql to get the list of files in a package.
	(diff1_package): Don't abort even if child diff1 returns 2.
	(rpm_report_diff): Use # as prefix for some of error messages.
	(rpm_retrieve_pkg): Pick only the first package in the packages list
	for a given file.

